java.lang.Comparable<Table>
public class Periodic
extends ObjectTable

The periodic table stores all registered periodics. Programs can remove periodics by simply deleting from this table. The compiler will translate all periodic statements within the program into a tuple entry that is registered in this table. The runtime schedules periodics from the tuple entries in this table.
